INSERT INTO `blog_essay` (`id`, `html`, `coverUrl`, `title`, `subtitle`, `digest`, `tags`, `domain`, `radio`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `upt_act`, `state`, `reading_num`) VALUES
(62, '<h2>如何自己实现一个npm init命令</h2><p><br></p><p>本篇文章将介绍如何自定义 &nbsp;npm init xxx命令，创建自己的脚手架</p><p><br></p><h3>一、初始化框架</h3><p><br></p><p>npm init，填好相关的信息后添加几个插件,并安装好依赖</p><pre><code class=\"language-javascript\">    \"fs-extra\": \"^11.2.0\",\n    \"inquirer\": \"^9.2.12\",\n    \"kolorist\": \"^1.8.0\"</code></pre><p><br></p><h3>二、具体思路</h3><p><br></p><p>具体可以参考vue-create的源码</p><p> <a href=\"https://github.com/vuejs/create-vue\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/vuejs/create-vue</a> </p><p><br></p><p>首先文件目录很简单，一个template，一个util &nbsp;,template存在模板，util存在处理文件的一些方法</p><p>先用inquirer插件获取用户的输入信息，比如</p><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2023/12/15/1702641860070475.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 100%;\"/></p><p>这边还有一个工具可以推荐使用一下，verdaccio，可以子啊本地开私有的nrm源，可以用来发包本地测试，具体使用可以csdn搜一下如何使用，挺简单的。</p><p>就是类似上图可以选择组件类型，然后可以询问项目名，描述，是否要测试模块等等。就比如我们npm init vite，也会问你使用vue3，还是react，是否需要支持ts等等。</p><p>获取到后，可以通过用户的回答来做判断。如果选中某个选项，就根据这个选项去到对应的template进行深度合并，当然，我们有一个最初始的模板，base，即没有选中任何选项之前，先渲染base，后面再根据选的选项进行和base合并，这边举我的例子</p><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2023/12/15/1702642186540274.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><p>先render(base),之后，如果我选了vue组件选项时，我就会render(component)，选需要单元测试，就render(test)，以此类推</p><p>render是个渲染函数。</p><p>直接上代码，</p><h3>根目录上创建index.js</h3><pre><code class=\"language-javascript\">#!/usr/bin/env node\n// index.js - 脚手架项目的主要代码文件\nimport inquirer from \'inquirer\';\nimport fs from \'fs-extra\';\nimport path from \'path\';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from \'url\';\nimport { getLoginUser } from \'./utils/user.js\';\nimport renderTemplate from \'./utils/renderTemplate.js\';\nimport { replaceVariablesInFiles } from \'./utils/file.js\';\nimport { red, yellow, bold, blue, gray } from \'kolorist\';\nconst __filename = fileURLToPath(import.meta.url);\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(__filename);\nasync function createNewProject() {\n  // 获取用户输入的信息\n  try {\n    var { cliType, name, description, version, author, test } =\n      await inquirer.prompt(\n        [\n          {\n            type: \'list\',\n            name: \'cliType\',\n            message: \'组件类型\',\n            default: 0,\n            choices: [\n              {\n                name: \'vue组件\',\n                value: \'component\'\n              },\n              {\n                name: \'js无界面组件\',\n                value: \'jsLibary\'\n              },\n              {\n                name: \'js动态界面组件\',\n                value: \'jsPage\'\n              }\n            ]\n          },\n          {\n            type: \'input\',\n            name: \'name\',\n            message: \'名称\'\n          },\n          {\n            type: \'input\',\n            name: \'version\',\n            required: false,\n            message: \'版本\',\n            default: \'0.1.0\'\n          },\n          {\n            type: \'input\',\n            name: \'description\',\n            message: \'描述\'\n          },\n          {\n            type: \'input\',\n            name: \'author\',\n            message: \'作者\',\n            default: getLoginUser\n          },\n          {\n            type: \'confirm\',\n            name: \'test\',\n            message: \'是否需要单元测试?\',\n            default: true\n          }\n        ],\n        {\n          onCancel: () =&gt; {\n            throw new Error(\'✖ \' + ` Operation cancelled`);\n          }\n        }\n      );\n  } catch (cancelled) {\n    console.log(cancelled.message);\n  }\n\n  // 新的项目目录\n  const root = path.join(process.cwd(), name);\n  // template目录\n  const templateRoot = path.join(__dirname, \'template\');\n  const callbacks = [];\n  // 格式化名称\n  function nameFormat(name) {\n    let firstStr = name.charAt(0).toUpperCase();\n    name = firstStr + name.substring(1);\n    let colIndex = name.indexOf(\'-\');\n    if (colIndex === -1) {\n      return name;\n    } else {\n      let afterIndex = colIndex + 1;\n      let afterStr = name.charAt(afterIndex);\n      if (afterStr) {\n        let upperStr = afterStr.toUpperCase();\n        let indexStr = name.substring(0, afterIndex);\n        name = indexStr + upperStr + name.substring(afterIndex + 1);\n        name = name.replace(\'-\', \'\');\n        return nameFormat(name);\n      } else {\n        name = name.replace(\'-\', \'\');\n        return name;\n      }\n    }\n  }\n  // 要替代的变量\n  const replacements = {\n    name,\n    varname: name.replace(/-/g, \'_\'),\n    fname: nameFormat(name),\n    description\n  };\n  const render = function render(templateName) {\n    const templateDir = path.resolve(templateRoot, templateName);\n    renderTemplate(templateDir, root, callbacks);\n  };\n  // 确保目录存在\n  fs.ensureDirSync(root);\n\n  // 将模板渲染到新目录上\n  render(\'base\');\n  if (cliType === \'component\') {\n    render(\'component\');\n  }\n  if (cliType === \'jsLibary\') {\n    render(\'jsLibary\');\n  }\n  if (cliType === \'jsPage\') {\n    render(\'jsPage\');\n  }\n  if (test) {\n    render(\'test\');\n  }\n  // 替换变量\n  replaceVariablesInFiles(root, replacements);\n\n  // 更新生成项目中的package.json\n  const packageJsonPath = path.join(root, \'package.json\');\n  const packageJson = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(packageJsonPath, \'utf-8\'));\n  packageJson.name = name;\n  packageJson.description = description;\n  packageJson.version = version;\n  packageJson.author = author;\n  fs.writeFileSync(packageJsonPath, JSON.stringify(packageJson, null, 2));\n  console.log(`\\n  Successfully created project ${yellow(name)}  \\n `);\n  console.log(`  ${gray(\'$\')} ${blue(`cd ${name}`)} `);\n  console.log(`  ${gray(\'$\')} ${blue(`npm i`)}`);\n  console.log(`  ${gray(\'$\')} ${blue(`npm run dev`)}    \\n `);\n}\n\ncreateNewProject();</code></pre><p>util的几个工具代码</p><h3>deepMerge深度合并脚本</h3><pre><code class=\"language-javascript\">const isObject = (val) =&gt; val && typeof val === \'object\';\nconst mergeArrayWithDedupe = (a, b) =&gt; Array.from(new Set([...a, ...b]));\n/**\n * Recursively merge the content of the new object to the existing one\n * @param {Object} target the existing object\n * @param {Object} obj the new object\n */\nconst deepMerge = function (target, obj) {\n  for (const key of Object.keys(obj)) {\n    const oldVal = target[key];\n    const newVal = obj[key];\n\n    if (Array.isArray(oldVal) && Array.isArray(newVal)) {\n      target[key] = mergeArrayWithDedupe(oldVal, newVal);\n    } else if (isObject(oldVal) && isObject(newVal)) {\n      target[key] = deepMerge(oldVal, newVal);\n    } else {\n      target[key] = newVal;\n    }\n  }\n\n  return target;\n};\n\nexport default deepMerge;\n</code></pre><h3>file.js文件操作脚本</h3><pre><code class=\"language-javascript\">/**\n * 文件操作工具类\n */\n\nimport fs from \'fs\';\nimport path from \'path\';\n\n// 是否存在该目录\nexport const existsDirMkdir = function (dir) {\n  if (!fs.existsSync(dir)) {\n    var basename = path.dirname(dir);\n    if (!fs.existsSync(basename)) {\n      existsDirMkdir(basename);\n    }\n    fs.mkdirSync(dir);\n  }\n};\n\n/**\n *\n * @param {String} directory 要替换变量的目录路径\n * @param {Object} replacements 要替换的所有变量名\n */\n// 替换目录所有文件的变量\nexport const replaceVariablesInFiles = function (directory, replacements) {\n  // 获取目录下所有文件和子目录\n  const files = fs.readdirSync(directory);\n\n  files.forEach((file) =&gt; {\n    const filePath = path.join(directory, file);\n    const stats = fs.statSync(filePath);\n\n    if (stats.isDirectory()) {\n      // 如果是子目录，则递归处理该目录下的文件\n      replaceVariablesInFiles(filePath, replacements);\n    } else {\n      // 如果是文件，则进行变量替换操作\n      let content = fs.readFileSync(filePath, \'utf8\');\n\n      for (const [key, value] of Object.entries(replacements)) {\n        const regex = new RegExp(`\\\\{\\\\{ ?${key} ?\\\\}\\\\}`, \'g\');\n        content = content.replace(regex, value);\n      }\n      fs.writeFileSync(filePath, content);\n    }\n  });\n};\n\nexport default {};\n</code></pre><h3>renderTemplate.js 渲染函数主要脚本</h3><pre><code class=\"language-javascript\">import * as fs from \'node:fs\';\nimport * as path from \'node:path\';\nimport { pathToFileURL } from \'node:url\';\n\nimport deepMerge from \'./deepMerge.js\';\nimport sortDependencies from \'./sortDependencies.js\';\n/**\n * Renders a template folder/file to the file system,\n * by recursively copying all files under the `src` directory,\n * with the following exception:\n *   - `_filename` should be renamed to `.filename`\n *   - Fields in `package.json` should be recursively merged\n * @param {string} src source filename to copy\n * @param {string} dest destination filename of the copy operation\n */\nconst renderTemplate = function (src, dest, callbacks) {\n  const stats = fs.statSync(src); // 获取对应路径下的文件/文件夹信息\n\n  if (stats.isDirectory()) { // 如果是一个文件夹\n    // skip node_module\n    if (path.basename(src) === \'node_modules\') { // node_modules不处理\n      return;\n    }\n\n    // if it\'s a directory, render its subdirectories and files recursively\n    // 如果是其他文件夹，则在目标路径下创建一个相应的文件夹，并递归子文件夹\n    fs.mkdirSync(dest, { recursive: true }); \n    for (const file of fs.readdirSync(src)) {\n      renderTemplate(\n        path.resolve(src, file),\n        path.resolve(dest, file),\n        callbacks\n      );\n    }\n    return;\n  }\n\n  const filename = path.basename(src);\n    // 如果文件名是 package.json，则读取已有的 dest 文件内容和新的 src 文件内容，并将两者进行深度合并\n  if (filename === \'package.json\' && fs.existsSync(dest)) {\n    // merge instead of overwriting\n    const existing = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(dest, \'utf8\'));\n    const newPackage = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(src, \'utf8\'));\n    const pkg = sortDependencies(deepMerge(existing, newPackage));\n    fs.writeFileSync(dest, JSON.stringify(pkg, null, 2) + \'\\n\');\n    return;\n  }\n\n  if (filename === \'extensions.json\' && fs.existsSync(dest)) {\n    // merge instead of overwriting\n    const existing = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(dest, \'utf8\'));\n    const newExtensions = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(src, \'utf8\'));\n    const extensions = deepMerge(existing, newExtensions);\n    fs.writeFileSync(dest, JSON.stringify(extensions, null, 2) + \'\\n\');\n    return;\n  }\n  // 如果文件名以 _ 开头，则将文件名中的 _ 替换为 .，然后根据新的名称在目标路径中创建一个相应的文件\n  if (filename.startsWith(\'_\')) {\n    // rename `_file` to `.file`\n    dest = path.resolve(path.dirname(dest), filename.replace(/^_/, \'.\'));\n  }\n\n  if (filename === \'_gitignore\' && fs.existsSync(dest)) {\n    // append to existing .gitignore\n    const existing = fs.readFileSync(dest, \'utf8\');\n    const newGitignore = fs.readFileSync(src, \'utf8\');\n    fs.writeFileSync(dest, existing + \'\\n\' + newGitignore);\n    return;\n  }\n\n  // data file for EJS templates\n  if (filename.endsWith(\'.data.mjs\')) {\n    // use dest path as key for the data store\n    dest = dest.replace(/\\.data\\.mjs$/, \'\');\n\n    // Add a callback to the array for late usage when template files are being processed\n    callbacks.push(async (dataStore) =&gt; {\n      const getData = (await import(pathToFileURL(src).toString())).default;\n\n      // Though current `getData` are all sync, we still retain the possibility of async\n      dataStore[dest] = await getData({\n        oldData: dataStore[dest] || {}\n      });\n    });\n\n    return; // skip copying the data file\n  }\n\n  fs.copyFileSync(src, dest);\n};\n\nexport default renderTemplate;\n</code></pre><h3>JSON排序脚本</h3><pre><code class=\"language-javascript\">/**\n * 对JSON文件进行排序处理\n * @param {JSON} packageJson // JSON文件\n * @returns\n */\nexport default function sortDependencies(packageJson) {\n  const sorted = {};\n\n  const depTypes = [\n    \'dependencies\',\n    \'devDependencies\',\n    \'peerDependencies\',\n    \'optionalDependencies\',\n    \'scripts\'\n  ];\n\n  for (const depType of depTypes) {\n    if (packageJson[depType]) {\n      sorted[depType] = {};\n      Object.keys(packageJson[depType])\n        .sort()\n        .forEach((name) =&gt; {\n          sorted[depType][name] = packageJson[depType][name];\n        });\n    }\n  }\n\n  return {\n    ...packageJson,\n    ...sorted\n  };\n}\n</code></pre><p>至于user.js跟这个没有关系，是处理默认用户的</p><p>值得说明的是有个替换变量的函数，</p><p>比如：</p><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2023/12/15/1702642632395379.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 100%;\"/></p><p>我们可以动态的把输入的信息放到模板上去，比如</p><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2023/12/15/1702642718229795.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 100%;\"/>我输入了名称，那么模板所有含{{name}}的都会被替换成这边的demo，当然，name是自己在index中定义好的，具体参见上面的</p><p>replaceVariablesInFiles函数和在index中使用它的方法</p><h3>这样我们就创建好啦！</h3><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2023/12/15/170264305019183.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 100%;\"/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>', '/public/uploads/2023/12/15/170264321968121.jpg', '创建npm init xxx 命令', '创建自己的组件模板', '看过很多模板，想着自己也创建一个命令，不用每次都修改默认的模板文件，可以通过选择自己设置的选项来初始化自己想要的模板。', 'node,js,npm', 'NODE', '1', '2023-12-15 20:26:59', '2023-12-15 20:26:59', 'U', 1, 21),
(63, '<p>1111</p><p><br></p>', '', '', '', '', '', 'NODE', '1', '2024-04-19 22:27:54', '2024-04-19 22:27:54', 'D', NULL, 0),
(64, '<p>111</p>', '', '', '', '', '', 'NODE', '1', '2024-04-19 22:33:31', '2024-04-19 22:33:31', 'D', NULL, 0),
(65, '<h1>react学习</h1><h3>1.基础语法</h3><p> &nbsp; &nbsp;a. jsx语法</p><p> &nbsp; &nbsp;b. 函数式组件</p><p><br></p><h3>2. hooks学习</h3><h3 style=\"text-align: start;\">useState</h3><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"background-color: var(--color-neutral-muted);\"><code>useState</code></span>用于在函数组件中添加状态管理功能。</p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><strong>使用案例：</strong></p><pre style=\"text-align: start;\"><code class=\"language-jsx\">import React, { useState } from \'react\';\n\nconst Counter = () =&gt; {\n  const [count, setCount] = useState(0);\n\n  const increment = () =&gt; {\n    setCount(count + 1);\n  };\n\n  const decrement = () =&gt; {\n    setCount(count - 1);\n  };\n\n  return (\n    &lt;div&gt;\n      &lt;p&gt;Count: {count}&lt;/p&gt;\n      &lt;button onClick={increment}&gt;Increment&lt;/button&gt;\n      &lt;button onClick={decrement}&gt;Decrement&lt;/button&gt;\n    &lt;/div&gt;\n  );\n};\n\nexport default Counter;\n</code></pre><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><strong>注意事项：</strong></p><ul><li style=\"text-align: start;\">使用数组解构来声明状态变量和更新函数。</li><li style=\"text-align: start;\">初始状态可以是基本类型数据（如数字、字符串、布尔值）或者是一个函数，用于惰性初始化状态。</li><li style=\"text-align: start;\">不要直接修改状态变量，而是通过提供的更新函数来更新状态。</li></ul><h3 style=\"text-align: start;\">useEffect</h3><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"background-color: var(--color-neutral-muted);\"><code>useEffect</code></span>用于在React函数组件中执行副作用操作，如数据获取、订阅、DOM操作等。</p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><strong>使用案例：</strong></p><pre style=\"text-align: start;\"><code class=\"language-jsx\">import React, { useState, useEffect } from \'react\';\n\nconst Timer = () =&gt; {\n  const [seconds, setSeconds] = useState(0);\n\n  useEffect(() =&gt; {\n    const interval = setInterval(() =&gt; {\n      setSeconds(prevSeconds =&gt; prevSeconds + 1);\n    }, 1000);\n\n    return () =&gt; clearInterval(interval);\n  }, []); // 空数组作为第二个参数表示只在组件挂载和卸载时执行\n\n  return (\n    &lt;div&gt;\n      &lt;p&gt;Timer: {seconds} seconds&lt;/p&gt;\n    &lt;/div&gt;\n  );\n};\n\nexport default Timer;\n</code></pre><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><strong>注意事项：</strong></p><ul><li style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"background-color: var(--color-neutral-muted);\"><code>useEffect</code></span>接受一个函数作为参数，该函数可以包含任何副作用操作。</li><li style=\"text-align: start;\">可选的第二个参数可以是依赖项数组，用来控制<span style=\"background-color: var(--color-neutral-muted);\"><code>useEffect</code></span>何时执行。</li><li style=\"text-align: start;\">返回一个清除函数用于清理副作用，比如清除定时器、取消订阅等。</li></ul><h3 style=\"text-align: start;\">useRef</h3><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"background-color: var(--color-neutral-muted);\"><code>useRef</code></span>用于在函数组件中创建一个可变的引用。</p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><strong>使用案例：</strong></p><pre style=\"text-align: start;\"><code class=\"language-jsx\">import React, { useRef } from \'react\';\n\nconst TextInput = () =&gt; {\n  const inputRef = useRef(null);\n\n  const focusInput = () =&gt; {\n    inputRef.current.focus();\n  };\n\n  return (\n    &lt;div&gt;\n      &lt;input ref={inputRef} type=\"text\" /&gt;\n      &lt;button onClick={focusInput}&gt;Focus Input&lt;/button&gt;\n    &lt;/div&gt;\n  );\n};\n\nexport default TextInput;\n</code></pre><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><strong>注意事项：</strong></p><ul><li style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"background-color: var(--color-neutral-muted);\"><code>useRef</code></span>返回一个可变的<span style=\"background-color: var(--color-neutral-muted);\"><code>{ current }</code></span> 属性，其初始值可以为任何值。</li><li style=\"text-align: start;\">主要用于访问DOM节点或者保存任何可变值，不会引起组件重新渲染。</li><li style=\"text-align: start;\">修改<span style=\"background-color: var(--color-neutral-muted);\"><code>useRef</code></span>的<span style=\"background-color: var(--color-neutral-muted);\"><code>current</code></span>属性不会引发重新渲染，因此可以作为存储任何可变值的容器</li></ul><h3>3. 组件传值</h3><p> &nbsp; &nbsp;props</p><pre><code class=\"language-jsx\">const ChildComponent = (props) =&gt; {\n    return &lt;div&gt;{props.message}&lt;/div&gt;;\n};\n\nconst ParentComponent = () =&gt; {\n    return &lt;ChildComponent message=\"Hello, World!\" /&gt;;\n};</code></pre><p>Context上下文传值</p><pre><code class=\"language-jsx\">const MyContext = React.createContext(defaultValue);\n\nconst ParentComponent = () =&gt; {\n    return (\n        &lt;MyContext.Provider value={/* some value */}&gt;\n            &lt;ChildComponent /&gt;\n        &lt;/MyContext.Provider&gt;\n    );\n};\n\nconst ChildComponent = () =&gt; {\n    const value = React.useContext(MyContext);\n    return &lt;div&gt;{value}&lt;/div&gt;;\n};\n</code></pre><p>回调函数</p><pre><code class=\"language-jsx\">const ParentComponent = () =&gt; {\n    const handleChildClick = (data) =&gt; {\n        console.log(data);\n    };\n\n    return &lt;ChildComponent onClick={handleChildClick} /&gt;;\n};\n\nconst ChildComponent = ({ onClick }) =&gt; {\n    const handleClick = () =&gt; {\n        onClick(\"Clicked from child!\");\n    };\n\n    return &lt;button onClick={handleClick}&gt;Click me&lt;/button&gt;;\n};\n</code></pre><p>hook</p><pre><code class=\"language-typescript\">const useCounter = (initialValue) =&gt; {\n    const [count, setCount] = React.useState(initialValue);\n\n    const increment = () =&gt; {\n        setCount(count + 1);\n    };\n\n    return { count, increment };\n};\n\nconst CounterComponent = () =&gt; {\n    const { count, increment } = useCounter(0);\n\n    return (\n        &lt;div&gt;\n            &lt;p&gt;Count: {count}&lt;/p&gt;\n            &lt;button onClick={increment}&gt;Increment&lt;/button&gt;\n        &lt;/div&gt;\n    );\n};\n</code></pre><p><br></p><p><br></p><h1>fishx</h1><h3>1.useFetch</h3><p><strong>基础用法</strong></p><pre><code class=\"language-jsx\">import { useFetch } from \'fishx\';\n\n// 用法 1\nconst { data, error, loading } = useFetch(\'/todos\');\n\n// 用法 2\nconst { data, error, loading } = useFetch({\n  url: \'/todos\',\n  method: \'post\',\n});\n\n// 用法 3\nconst { data, error, loading } = useFetch((userId) =&gt; `/todos/${userId}`);\n\n// 用法 4\nconst { loading, run } = useFetch((username) =&gt; ({\n  url: \'/api/changeUsername\',\n  method: \'post\',\n  data: { username },\n}), {\n  manual: true,\n});</code></pre><p>参数功能介绍：</p><p><strong>轮询</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\">通过设置 <span style=\"color: var(--ifm-code-color); background-color: var(--ifm-code-background);\"><code>options.pollingInterval</code></span> ，进入轮询模式，定时触发函数执行。</p><ul><li style=\"text-align: start;\">通过设置 <span style=\"color: var(--ifm-code-color); background-color: var(--ifm-code-background);\"><code>options.pollingWhenHidden=false</code></span> ，在屏幕不可见时，暂时暂停定时任务。</li><li style=\"text-align: start;\">通过 <span style=\"color: var(--ifm-code-color); background-color: var(--ifm-code-background);\"><code>run / cancel</code></span> 来 开启/停止 轮询。</li><li style=\"text-align: start;\">在 <span style=\"color: var(--ifm-code-color); background-color: var(--ifm-code-background);\"><code>options.manual=true</code></span> 时，需要第一次执行 <span style=\"color: var(--ifm-code-color); background-color: var(--ifm-code-background);\"><code>run</code></span> 后，才开始轮询。</li></ul><pre><code class=\"language-jsx\">import { useFetch } from \'fishx\';\nimport { Button, Spin } from \'@whalecloud/fdx\';\nimport React from \'react\';\nimport Mock from \'mockjs\';\n\nfunction getUsername(): Promise&lt;string&gt; {\n  return new Promise(resolve =&gt; {\n    setTimeout(() =&gt; {\n      resolve(Mock.mock(\'@name\'));\n    }, 1000);\n  });\n}\n\nexport default () =&gt; {\n  const { data, loading, run, cancel } = useFetch(getUsername, {\n    pollingInterval: 1000,\n    pollingWhenHidden: false\n  })\n\n  return (\n    &lt;&gt;\n      &lt;Spin spinning={loading}&gt;\n        &lt;p&gt;Username: {data}&lt;/p&gt;\n      &lt;/Spin&gt;\n      &lt;Button.Group&gt;\n        &lt;Button onClick={run}&gt;start&lt;/Button&gt;\n        &lt;Button onClick={cancel}&gt;stop&lt;/Button&gt;\n      &lt;/Button.Group&gt;\n    &lt;/&gt;\n  )\n}</code></pre><p><br></p><p><strong>防抖和节流</strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(28, 30, 33);\">通过设置 </span>options.debounceInterval<span style=\"color: rgb(28, 30, 33);\"> ，则进入防抖模式。此时如果频繁触发 </span>run<span style=\"color: rgb(28, 30, 33);\">，则会以防抖策略进行请求。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(28, 30, 33);\">通过设置 </span>options.throttleInterval<span style=\"color: rgb(28, 30, 33);\"> ，则进入节流模式。此时如果频繁触发 </span>run<span style=\"color: rgb(28, 30, 33);\"> ，则会以节流策略进行请求。</span></p><p><br></p><pre><code class=\"language-jsx\">import { useFetch } from \'fishx\';\nimport { Select } from \'@whalecloud/fdx\';\nimport React from \'react\';\nimport Mock from \'mockjs\';\n\nconst { Option } = Select;\n\nasync function getEmail(search: string): Promise&lt;string[]&gt; {\n  console.log(search);\n  return new Promise(resolve =&gt; {\n    setTimeout(() =&gt; {\n      resolve(Mock.mock({ \'data|5\': [\'@email\'] }).data);\n    }, 300);\n  });\n}\n\nexport default () =&gt; {\n  const { data, loading, run, cancel } = useFetch(getEmail, {\n    debounceInterval: 500,\n    throttleInterval: 500,\n    manual: true\n  });\n\n  return (\n    &lt;div&gt;\n      &lt;p&gt;Enter quickly to see the effect&lt;/p&gt;\n      &lt;Select\n        showSearch\n        placeholder=\"Select Emails\"\n        filterOption={false}\n        onSearch={run}\n        onBlur={cancel}\n        loading={loading}\n        style={{ width: 300 }}\n      &gt;\n        {data && data.map(i =&gt; &lt;Option key={i}&gt;{i}&lt;/Option&gt;)}\n      &lt;/Select&gt;\n    &lt;/div&gt;\n  );\n};</code></pre><p><strong>拦截器</strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(28, 30, 33);\">下面的示例中 把请求头进行拦截，并修改为 </span>headers<span style=\"color: rgb(28, 30, 33);\"> 请求格式为 </span>\'application/x-www-form-urlencoded; charset=UTF-8\'<span style=\"color: rgb(28, 30, 33);\">。</span></p><pre><code class=\"language-jsx\">function handleRequest(config: any) {\n  config.headers = {\n    ...config.headers,\n    ...{\'content-type\': \'application/x-www-form-urlencoded; charset=UTF-8\'}\n  }\n  return config\n}\n\nconst config = {\n  rest: {\n    endpoint: \'http://172.21.33.100:9933\',\n    interceptor: {\n      requests: [handleRequest],\n    }\n  },\n}\n\nexport default config</code></pre><h3>2.router路由</h3><p><strong>路由配置</strong></p><p> &nbsp; &nbsp;约定式路由</p><pre><code class=\"language-javascript\">[\n  { path: \'/\', component: \'./pages/index.js\' },\n  { path: \'/users/\', component: \'./pages/users/index.js\' },\n  { path: \'/users/list\', component: \'./pages/users/list.js\' },\n]</code></pre><p> &nbsp; &nbsp;配置式路由</p><pre><code class=\"language-typescript\">[\n  { path: \'/\', component: \'./pages/index.js\' },\n  { path: \'/users/:id\', component: \'./pages/users/$id.js\' },\n  { path: \'/:post/\', component: \'./pages/$post/index.js\' },\n  { path: \'/:post/comments\', component: \'./pages/$post/comments.js\' },\n]</code></pre><p><strong>&lt;Link&gt;</strong></p><pre><code class=\"language-jsx\">import React from \'react\'\nimport { Link } from \'fishx\'\n\nexport default () =&gt; (\n  &lt;div&gt;\n    &lt;h1&gt;Home Page&lt;/h1&gt;\n    &lt;nav&gt;\n      &lt;Link to=\"/\"&gt;Home&lt;/Link&gt;\n      &lt;span&gt; | &lt;/span&gt;\n      &lt;Link to=\"/about\"&gt;About&lt;/Link&gt;\n    &lt;/nav&gt;\n  &lt;/div&gt;\n)</code></pre><p><strong>使用history</strong></p><pre><code class=\"language-jsx\">import React from \"react\";\nimport { useHistory } from \'fishx\';\n\nfunction HomeButton() {\n  let history = useHistory()\n\n  function handleClick() {\n    history.push(\'/home\')\n  }\n\n  return (\n    &lt;button type=\"button\" onClick={handleClick as any}&gt;\n      Go home\n    &lt;/button&gt;\n  )\n}\n\nexport default HomeButton</code></pre><p><strong>路由参数</strong></p><p>配置参数</p><pre><code class=\"language-jsx\">const routes = [\n  {\n    path: \'/\',\n    component: \'./index\',\n    exact: true,\n  },\n  {\n    path: \'/user/:name\',\n    component: \'./User\',\n    exact: true,\n  },\n];\n\nexport default routes;</code></pre><p>获取参数</p><pre><code class=\"language-jsx\">import React from \'react\'\nimport { useParams } from \'fishx\';\n\nconst User = () =&gt; {\n  const { name } = useParams()\n  return (\n    &lt;div className=\"user\"&gt;\n      &lt;h1&gt;Hey, I am {name} &lt;/h1&gt;\n    &lt;/div&gt;\n  )\n}\n\nexport default User;</code></pre><p><strong>权限路由</strong></p><p>FishX<span style=\"color: rgb(28, 30, 33);\"> 的权限路由是通过配置路由的 </span>Routes<span style=\"color: rgb(28, 30, 33);\"> 属性来实现。</span></p><pre><code class=\"language-javascript\">[\n  { \n    path: \'/\',\n    component: \'./pages/index.js\',\n  },\n  {\n    path: \'/list\',\n    component: \'./pages/list.js\',\n    Routes: [\'./components/Authorized\'],\n  },\n]</code></pre><h3>3.国际化</h3><p><span style=\"color: rgb(28, 30, 33);\">在构建配置文件 </span>fishx.config.ts<span style=\"color: rgb(28, 30, 33);\"> 配置：</span></p><pre><code class=\"language-jsx\">import { LocalePlugin } from \'@fishx/plugins\';\n\nconst config = {\n  plugins: [\n    new LocalePlugin(),\n  ],\n};\n\nexport default config;</code></pre><p>设置目录</p><pre><code >...\n├── src\n│   ...\n│   ├── locale\n│   │   ├── en_US\n│   │   │   ├── hello.json\n│   │   │   └── simple.json\n│   │   └── zh_CN\n│   │       ├── hello.json\n│   │       └── simple.json\n│   ...\n...\n</code></pre><p>加上对应的翻译</p><pre><code class=\"language-jsx\">// zh_CN\n{\n  \"HELLO_GREETING\": \"你好Fish\",\n  \"HELLO_SIMPLE\": \"谢谢！\",\n  \"HELLO_REDUX\": \"我是由react-intl-universal翻译的\",\n  \"HELLO_DIFF\": \"你好, {name}. 欢迎来到 {where}!\"\n}</code></pre><pre><code class=\"language-jsx\">// en_US\n{\n  \"HELLO_GREETING\": \"Hello I am fish\",\n  \"HELLO_SIMPLE\": \"Thanks you!\",\n  \"HELLO_REDUX\": \"I am translate by react-intl-universal\",\n  \"HELLO_DIFF\": \"Hello, {name}. Welcome to {where}!\"\n}</code></pre><h3>4.状态管理</h3><p> <a href=\"https://fish.iwhalecloud.com/fishx-desktop-v2/fishx/docs/store/redux\" target=\"_blank\">https://fish.iwhalecloud.com/fishx-desktop-v2/fishx/docs/store/redux</a> </p><p><br></p><h1>electron</h1><p><strong>概念：</strong></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><h1>ts学习</h1><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><h1>git流程规范</h1><p><br></p><p>正常流程：从任务单中的release拉取特性分支</p><p><img src=\"http://1.94.31.132:7001/public/uploads/2024/07/29/1722232528551266.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><p> &nbsp; &nbsp;创建合并请求</p><p><img src=\"http://1.94.31.132:7001/public/uploads/2024/07/29/1722232814406365.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><p>冲突解决：从需要合并的分支中创建临时分支</p><p><img src=\"http://1.94.31.132:7001/public/uploads/2024/07/29/1722242237271330.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><p>拉取自需要合并的分支，进行每个文件的冲突解决</p><p><img src=\"http://1.94.31.132:7001/public/uploads/2024/07/29/1722242291130923.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><p>冲突解决后再从临时分支合并到dev分支</p><p><br></p><ol><li>开发自测：<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">release-&gt;拉取特性分支开发-&gt;创建合并请求到develop-&gt;部署开发环境自测</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">版本提测：特性分支-&gt;合并到master分支 -&gt;部署测试环境测试</span></li><ol><li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">测试有问题，在原单的特性分支修复，合到develop自测，合到master复测</span></li></ol><li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">版本发布：特性 -&gt;合并release -&gt;CMO发布release分支</span></li></ol><p><br></p><h1>公司组件使用</h1><p>1.tableAndSearch</p><p> &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>基本参数</strong></p><p> &nbsp; &nbsp;tableConfig：表格列表参数</p><p> &nbsp; &nbsp;searchFormConfig：搜索条件过滤</p><p> &nbsp; &nbsp;handleRef：调用子组件方法（onFresh，onReset等）</p><pre><code class=\"language-html\">&lt;TableAndSearch tableConfig={tableConfig} searchFormConfig={searchFormConfig} onRef={handleRef} /&gt;</code></pre><p> &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong> 按钮权限 & 按钮过滤</strong></p><pre><code class=\"language-jsx\">   const dynamicCustAction = (record: any) =&gt; {\n  // 定义状态和对应的操作映射\n    const statusActions: Record&lt;string, Array&lt;any&gt;&gt; = {\n      draft: [\n        { key: \'view\', type: tableIconMap.VIEW, name: i18n(\'COMMON_DETAIL\'), permissionCode: EVENT_TRIGGER_CAMPAIGN.VIEW },\n        { key: \'edit\', type: tableIconMap.EDIT, name: i18n(\'COMMON_EDIT\'), permissionCode: EVENT_TRIGGER_CAMPAIGN.EDIT },\n        { key: \'pilot\', type: tableIconMap.CLOCK, name: i18n(\'EVENT_TRIGGER_STATUS_PILOT\'), permissionCode: EVENT_TRIGGER_CAMPAIGN.PILOT },\n      ],\n      open: [\n        { key: \'view\', type: tableIconMap.VIEW, name: i18n(\'COMMON_DETAIL\'), permissionCode: EVENT_TRIGGER_CAMPAIGN.VIEW },\n        { key: \'pause\', type: tableIconMap.SUSPEND, name: i18n(\'EVENT_TRIGGER_STATUS_PAUSE\'), permissionCode: EVENT_TRIGGER_CAMPAIGN.PAUSE },\n      ],\n      pilot: [\n        { key: \'view\', type: tableIconMap.VIEW, name: i18n(\'COMMON_DETAIL\'), permissionCode: EVENT_TRIGGER_CAMPAIGN.VIEW },\n        { key: \'pause\', type: tableIconMap.SUSPEND, name: i18n(\'EVENT_TRIGGER_STATUS_PAUSE\'), permissionCode: EVENT_TRIGGER_CAMPAIGN.PAUSE },\n        { key: \'open\', type: tableIconMap.START, name: i18n(\'EVENT_TRIGGER_STATUS_OPEN\'), permissionCode: EVENT_TRIGGER_CAMPAIGN.OPEN },\n      ],\n      pilot_pause: [\n        { key: \'view\', type: tableIconMap.VIEW, name: i18n(\'COMMON_DETAIL\'), permissionCode: EVENT_TRIGGER_CAMPAIGN.VIEW },\n        { key: \'pilot_resume\', type: tableIconMap.START, name: i18n(\'EVENT_TRIGGER_STATUS_OPEN\'), permissionCode: EVENT_TRIGGER_CAMPAIGN.RESUME },\n      ],\n      open_pause: [\n        { key: \'view\', type: tableIconMap.VIEW, name: i18n(\'COMMON_DETAIL\'), permissionCode: EVENT_TRIGGER_CAMPAIGN.VIEW },\n        { key: \'open_resume\', type: tableIconMap.START, name: i18n(\'EVENT_TRIGGER_STATUS_OPEN\'), permissionCode: EVENT_TRIGGER_CAMPAIGN.RESUME },\n      ],\n      default: [\n        { key: \'view\', type: tableIconMap.VIEW, name: i18n(\'COMMON_DETAIL\'), permissionCode: EVENT_TRIGGER_CAMPAIGN.VIEW },\n      ],\n    };\n    // 根据record.campaignStatus获取对应的操作项，若未找到则使用default\n    const actions = statusActions[record.campaignStatus] || statusActions.default;\n    return actions;\n  };</code></pre><p> <strong> &nbsp; &nbsp;国际化页面</strong></p><p> &nbsp; &nbsp;引入i18n，在locale中具体的json文件中配置需要国际化的文字。</p><p> &nbsp; &nbsp;注意需要在方法内使用该插件，否则会有显示bug</p><pre><code >import { i18n, i18n as $t } from \'@fishx/i18n\';</code></pre><p><strong> &nbsp; 按钮点击 & 异步弹框</strong></p><p> &nbsp; 通过try catch的方式可以触发异步loading</p><pre><code class=\"language-jsx\"> const handleOperation = (key: string, record: any,) =&gt; {\n    console.log(key);\n    if (key === \'view\') {\n      return history.push(`/eventTriggerCampaign/${operationType.VIEW}?campaignId=${record?.campaignId}`);\n    } if (key === \'edit\') {\n      return history.push(`/eventTriggerCampaign/${operationType.EDIT}?campaignId=${record?.campaignId}`);\n    } if (key === \'open\') {\n      Modal.warning({\n        title: $t(\'EVENT_TRIGGER_CHANGE_STATUS_TIPS\'),\n        okText: $t(\'COMMON_CONFIRM\'),\n        cancelText: $t(\'COMMON_CANCEL\'),\n        centered: true,\n        okCancel: true,\n        async onOk() {\n          try {\n            return await new Promise(async (resolve, reject) =&gt; {\n              const res = await openCampaign({ campaignId: record.campaignId });\n              if (res) {\n                message.success($t(\'EVENT_TRIGGER_MODIFY_SUCCESSFULLY\'));\n                handleRef.current?.onRefresh();\n                return resolve(\'\');\n              }\n              return reject(new Error(\'\'));\n            });\n          } catch {\n            return console.log(\'Oops errors!\');\n          }\n        },\n      });\n    } if (key === \'open_resume\' || key === \'pilot_resume\') {\n      Modal.warning({\n        title: $t(\'EVENT_TRIGGER_CHANGE_STATUS_TIPS\'),\n        okText: $t(\'COMMON_CONFIRM\'),\n        cancelText: $t(\'COMMON_CANCEL\'),\n        centered: true,\n        okCancel: true,\n        async onOk() {\n          try {\n            return await new Promise(async (resolve, reject) =&gt; {\n              const res = await resumeCampaign({ campaignId: record.campaignId });\n              if (res) {\n                message.success($t(\'EVENT_TRIGGER_MODIFY_SUCCESSFULLY\'));\n                handleRef.current?.onRefresh();\n                return resolve(\'\');\n              }\n              return reject(new Error(\'\'));\n            });\n          } catch {\n            return console.log(\'Oops errors!\');\n          }\n        },\n      });\n    } if (key === \'pause\') {\n      Modal.warning({\n        title: $t(\'EVENT_TRIGGER_CHANGE_STATUS_TIPS\'),\n        okText: $t(\'COMMON_CONFIRM\'),\n        cancelText: $t(\'COMMON_CANCEL\'),\n        centered: true,\n        okCancel: true,\n        async onOk() {\n          try {\n            return await new Promise(async (resolve, reject) =&gt; {\n              const res = await pauseCampaign({ campaignId: record.campaignId });\n              if (res) {\n                message.success($t(\'EVENT_TRIGGER_MODIFY_SUCCESSFULLY\'));\n                handleRef.current?.onRefresh();\n                return resolve(\'\');\n              }\n              return reject(new Error(\'\'));\n            });\n          } catch {\n            return console.log(\'Oops errors!\');\n          }\n        },\n      });\n    } if (key === \'pilot\') {\n      Modal.warning({\n        title: $t(\'EVENT_TRIGGER_CHANGE_STATUS_TIPS\'),\n        okText: $t(\'COMMON_CONFIRM\'),\n        cancelText: $t(\'COMMON_CANCEL\'),\n        centered: true,\n        okCancel: true,\n        async onOk() {\n          try {\n            return await new Promise(async (resolve, reject) =&gt; {\n              const res = await pilotCampaign({ campaignId: record.campaignId });\n              if (res) {\n                message.success($t(\'EVENT_TRIGGER_MODIFY_SUCCESSFULLY\'));\n                handleRef.current?.onRefresh();\n                return resolve(\'\');\n              }\n              return reject(new Error(\'\'));\n            });\n          } catch {\n            return console.log(\'Oops errors!\');\n          }\n        },\n      });\n    }\n    return null;\n  };</code></pre><p> &nbsp;<strong> &nbsp; 自定义参数</strong></p><p><strong> &nbsp; &nbsp; </strong>可以通过自定义请求 ，返回promise时，传回改变的参数</p><pre><code class=\"language-jsx\">  const queryTable = (params:any) =&gt; {\n    let date = {};\n    Object.keys(params).forEach(key =&gt; {\n      if (key.includes(\'schedule\')) {\n        date = { ...date, ...getDateFromTo(params[key], key) };\n      }\n    });\n    return queryCampaign({ ...params, ...date }).then(res =&gt; {\n      const { list, pageBean } = res;\n      const result = list.map((item:any) =&gt;\n        ({ ...item, key: item.campaignId })\n      );\n      \n      return { list: result, pageBean };\n    });\n  };</code></pre><p><strong> &nbsp; &nbsp; 字典使用</strong></p><p><strong> &nbsp;</strong> &nbsp; 通过useDict获取后台字典数据，并通过从后端给的CODE获取前端需要的字典数据。</p><pre><code class=\"language-jsx\">import useDict, { DICT_TYPE_CODE } from \'@/hooks/useDict\';\n  const { data: campaignStatus } = useDict({\n    dictType: DICT_TYPE_CODE.MARKETING_CAMPAIGN_STATUS,\n  });</code></pre><p><strong> &nbsp; &nbsp; 格式化时间戳</strong></p><p> &nbsp; &nbsp;通过moment函数把需要的时间格式化成时间戳的形式，解决因时区不同显示不同时间的问题</p><pre><code class=\"language-jsx\">  import moment from \'moment\';\n  const getDateFromTo = (data: [null, null], key: string) =&gt; {\n    const startTime = data?.[0] && moment(data?.[0]).startOf(\'day\').format(\'x\');\n    const endTime = data?.[1] && moment(data?.[1]).endOf(\'day\').format(\'x\');\n    const params = {\n      startTime: startTime ? startTime * 1 : null,\n      endTime: endTime ? endTime * 1 : null,\n      [key]: undefined,\n    };\n    return params;\n  };</code></pre><p><br></p><h1>antd</h1><p>样式修改规则：</p><p>在 <span style=\"color: rgb(78, 201, 176);\">Select &nbsp;Dropdown &nbsp;</span>这种创建在根元素root之外的下拉框类型元素，直接修改它的样式是不行的，需要用styles.类型去包裹</p><p>要注意的是，它们不能直接用className进行命名，而是要用它们的特定class属性进行命名，例如：</p><p><br></p><pre><code class=\"language-jsx\">      &lt;Select\n            options={LANGUAGES}\n            onChange={onLanguageChange}\n            value={currentLanguage}\n            bordered={false}\n            popupClassName={styles[\'custom-dropdown-menu\']}\n          /&gt;\n      &lt;Dropdown overlayClassName={styles[\'custom-dropdown-menu\']} menu={{ items: menuItems, onClick }} placement=\"bottomRight\"&gt;\n        &lt;EllipsisOutlined onClick={stopPropagation} /&gt;\n      &lt;/Dropdown&gt;</code></pre><pre><code class=\"language-css\">.custom-dropdown-menu {\n  :global {\n    .antd4-select-item-option-selected:not(.antd4-select-item-option-disabled) {\n      background: #EAEEFC !important;\n    }\n\n    .antd4-select-item-option {\n      background: #fff !important;\n    }\n\n    .antd4-select-item-option:hover {\n      background: #EAEEFC !important;\n    }\n  }\n}\n\n.custom-dropdown-menu {\n  :global {\n    .antd4-dropdown-menu-item-active {\n      background: #EAEEFC !important;\n    }\n  }\n}</code></pre><p><br></p><h1>ahook</h1><p>userequest</p><p>简单举例：</p><p>manual：是否手动执行，false时，会在一开始就执行一次</p><p>onSuccess：可传回response和params，有个小注意点，params只传入外部传入的，如下第一个例子，只能获取...params，而自己额外传入的auditId,<br>auditState: AUDIT_STATE.PASS这两个默认传参，则是拿不到的</p><pre><code class=\"language-jsx\">  const { loading: audioLoading, runAsync: doAudio } = useRequest(\r\n    (params: Partial&lt;AuditParams&gt; = {}) =&gt;\r\n      audit({\r\n        auditId,\r\n        auditState: AUDIT_STATE.PASS,\r\n        ...params,\r\n      }),\r\n    {\r\n      manual: true,\r\n      onSuccess(res, params:any) {\r\n        if (res?.resultCode === \'0\') {\r\n          if (params[0]?.auditState === AUDIT_STATE.REJECT) {\r\n            message.success(i18n(\'MERCHANT_AUDIT_REJECTED_SUCCESSFULLY\'));\r\n          } else {\r\n            message.success(i18n(\'MERCHANT_AUDIT_APPROVED_SUCCESSFULLY\'));\r\n          }\r\n          Fishx.history.goBack();\r\n        }\r\n      },\r\n      onError(error) {\r\r\r\n        message.error(error?.nativeBody?.resultMsg);\r\n      },\r\n    },\r\n  );\n  const { run: runSendOtp, loading } = useRequest(sendOtp, {\r\n    manual: true,\r\n    onSuccess: res =&gt; {\r\n      const { resultCode, result } = res.data;\r\n      if (resultCode === \'0\') {\r\n        setErrorPromptVisible(false);\r\n        setSecurityId(result?.securityId);\r\n        setStep(STEP.VAERIFY);\r\n      } else {\r\n        if (resultCode === \'ECOMMERCE-MEMBER-03504\') {\r\n          setErrorPromptVisible(true);\r\n          setStep(STEP.VAERIFY);\r\n          return;\r\n        }\r\n        setErrorMsg(res?.data?.resultMsg);\r\n      }\r\n    },\r\n  });</code></pre><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>', '/public/uploads/2024/07/23/1721726589303782.jpg', '学习文档', '技术学习，了解业务', '1. react：基础语法，hooks学习。  \n2. fishx：主要是useFetch，路由（配置，useHistory），国际化，状态管理(redux) 的学习\n3. electron的了解。\n4. ts基础学习。\n5. git流程使用规范。\n6. antd使用学习（表单和表格的配置）。\n4. 熟悉业务，包括商户列表，campaignEvent(活动列表)等', 'react', 'REACT', '1', '2024-07-18 17:10:28', '2024-07-18 17:10:28', 'U', 1, 96),
(66, '<h1>业务方面</h1><p><br></p><h3>toka是什么？</h3><p> <a href=\"https://ogtd9v.yuque.com/dxnwzg/kc51bx/kgv9lxxsqnwlud3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://ogtd9v.yuque.com/dxnwzg/kc51bx/kgv9lxxsqnwlud3d</a> </p><p><br></p><p>工作流程：</p><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2024/08/20/1724136868721962.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><h3>7月工作内容</h3><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2024/08/13/1723533092692939.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 100%;\"/></p><h3><strong>运营平台：</strong></h3><h3><strong>event trigger campaign 活动管理</strong></h3><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2024/08/13/1723533256561133.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 50%;\"/><img src=\"http://1.94.31.132:7001/public/uploads/2024/08/13/172353326756283.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><p>当用户触发事件触发活动中设置的条件，并允许用户享受活动时，系统将自动向用户账户发放奖品。</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"http://1.94.31.132:7001/public/uploads/2024/08/20/1724136807475529.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><p><br></p><h3><strong>System Q&As</strong></h3><p><img src=\"http://1.94.31.132:7001/public/uploads/2024/08/13/1723533390806946.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2024/08/13/172353343625055.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 676.50px;height: 494.69px;\"/><img src=\"http://1.94.31.132:7001/public/uploads/2024/08/13/1723533395613227.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><p>用户在探索过程中遇到问题时，可以在APP中查看和搜索系统问答。</p><p>1. 用户可以先进入“我的个人资料”页面，然后进入“帮助与支持”页面，点击“系统问答”按钮，浏览系统问答</p><p>2. 在系统问答页面，用户可以搜索关键字，也可以直接点击相应的目录进行查找。</p><p>3. 用户单击，查看系统问答</p><p><img src=\"http://1.94.31.132:7001/public/uploads/2024/08/20/172413682605369.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/><img src=\"http://1.94.31.132:7001/public/uploads/2024/08/20/1724136828486452.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/><img src=\"http://1.94.31.132:7001/public/uploads/2024/08/20/1724136830402106.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/><img src=\"http://1.94.31.132:7001/public/uploads/2024/08/20/1724136832304821.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><h3><strong>商户审批列表</strong></h3><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2024/08/13/1723533486017430.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 50%;\"/><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2024/08/13/172353350598159.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 505.50px;height: 318.56px;\"/></p><p>每一笔审批的单据都应该可追溯，可以查看历史的审批记录</p><h3><strong>商户平台：</strong></h3><h3>商户申请列表</h3><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2024/08/13/172353356922618.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><p>流程：</p><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2024/08/20/1724138026567415.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><h3><strong>小程序模块</strong></h3><p>小程序这边主要帮助移动端进行jsApi的测试，主要包括会用到的jsApi以及一些我们自定义的jsApi，比如my.call(\'pay\'),支付能力，my.call(\'getAuthCode\')获取用户信息。</p><p>帮助创建页面点击场景以及流程来帮助测试jsApi的能力。</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>', '/public/uploads/2024/08/14/1723625399463989.jpg', '7月业务开发', '学习', '7月业务开发学习内容', 'react', 'REACT', '1', '2024-08-13 15:26:24', '2024-08-13 15:26:24', 'D', 2, 134),
(67, '<h1>业务方面</h1><p><br></p><h3>toka是什么？</h3><p> TOKA是墨西哥一家持有金融科技牌照的企业，同时当前主要营收来自于以企业为主，给员工发放pantry卡、礼品卡、油卡等业务，我们基本不面向个人用户。综合来说，toka是以YAK收单行业核心(自研)、小程序平台(A+)，以及第三方支付账务核心(宝付)为TOKA建设一套综合行业收单及支付解决方案，项目对外称为“TokaPay” 钱包。</p><p>主要分为3端:</p><p><strong>APP端：</strong></p><p>APP端是用户端，即Toka APP，用户通过该APP进行使用移动支付，商户等业务</p><p><strong>商户端:</strong></p><p>商户端是面向商家的，商家在该系统入驻商户后，可以管理门店，员工，设备等操作。是收款系统的业务实体之一，钱包系统为其收款</p><p><strong>运营端（BO系统）:</strong></p><p>BO端即后台管理系统，是管理所有系统即设置的端口，管理员可以在这边对Toka APP，商户管理系统，商户APP等所有设置做出管理操作</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>工作流程：</p><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2024/08/20/1724136868721962.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><h3>8月工作内容</h3><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2024/10/15/1728995377459424.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><h3><strong>T&C协议模块</strong></h3><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2024/10/15/1728995410331786.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 100%;\"/>在账号密码无误的情况下去检查协议是否有更新，如有更新，需要重新签署协议</p><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2024/10/15/1728995417979434.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><p>全部勾选后可进行签署并直接登录进系统，再次登录时就不用再重新签署相同的协议了</p><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2024/10/15/1728995435924132.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2024/10/15/1728995439327401.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><p><br></p><p>更新的协议则在BO运营系统进行管理，点击tab页对应的商户协议管理，有对应的英语和西语的协议版本</p><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2024/10/15/1728995452664232.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><p>要更新版本时，则可以添加版本更高的协议，并上传html格式的文件，上传成功后第二天生效</p><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2024/10/15/172899546225827.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><h3>商户门店模块</h3><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2024/10/15/1728995561034893.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><p>登录账号后查看对应权限的门店列表</p><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2024/10/15/1728995581832296.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><p>我们来新增一个门店，填写相应的信息，包括名称，经营时间，联系方式，经纬度，地区区域，照片等</p><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2024/10/15/1728995591773536.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2024/10/15/1728995594696667.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><p>在门店列表，主要可以对应管理门店下的设备，点击设备按钮后，会跳转设备列表，并且默认带上该门店的ID进行查询，从而进行管理。</p><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2024/10/15/1728995604861264.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2024/10/15/1728995607201566.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><p>其次是对门店的开放和下架进行管理，点击激活和下架按钮会在状态之间进行切换并刷新</p><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2024/10/15/172899561599464.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><p>需要注意的是，当运营BO系统的管理员对该门店进行下架过的，商户的管理员便不能对其重新开放，因为BO具有更高的权限，且状态不会因此紊乱</p><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2024/10/15/1728995623418892.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2024/10/15/1728995626717628.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><p>其次是门店删除，我们只对没有员工绑定的门店进行删除，如果该门店还存在员工，则会对其进行提示先处理门店中的员工。</p><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2024/10/15/1728995637881110.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2024/10/15/1728995640430107.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><h3>商户详情模块</h3><p>商户详情是作为商户注册时填写的信息，并在登录时可以在商户页中进行查看详情，主要包括商户的一些具体信息（包括基础，KYB，财政），以及静态收款码，合约信息，开发配置等</p><p><br></p><ul><li>KYB：<span style=\"color: rgb(20, 21, 26); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px;\">Know Your Business &nbsp;商户的认证过程</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(20, 21, 26); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px;\">KYC：Know Your Customer 用户的认证过程</span></li></ul><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2024/10/15/1728995659092674.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><p><br></p><p>这边主要看我做的模块</p><p>QRcode主要展示和下载商户的收款二维码，需要注意的是如果没有签署任何有关“\'Standard CScanB Static QR Payment”产品的合约，则该二维码是不生效的并会给出提示</p><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2024/10/15/1728995679827234.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><p>development setting主要展示开发时需要的公钥管理，每个公钥对应一个有效合约的产品，商户配置public-key之后，走openApi接口的时候 外部网关发现类型是商户的就会根据clientId去拿对应的生效公钥进行验签</p><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2024/10/15/1728995688162213.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><h3>文档输出</h3><p><a href=\"https://ogtd9v.yuque.com/dxnwzg/kc51bx/eaahu88wkbrikywa\" target=\"_blank\">Event Trigger Campaign</a></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>', '/public/uploads/2024/10/15/1728995487896510.jpg', '8月工作业务', '业务学习', '业务陈述，主要通过日常开发的内容以及一些流程图来结合整合，帮助业务上的学习。', 'react', 'REACT', '1', '2024-10-15 20:36:36', '2024-10-15 20:36:36', 'D', 2, 36),
(68, '<h3>首页：<img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2024/11/07/1730973812142644.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 100%;\"/></h3>', '/public/uploads/2024/11/07/1730973869599376.png', '博客UI改动', 'UI更新记录', '根据以往UI去总结修改样式', 'blog', '其他', '1', '2024-11-07 18:04:30', '2024-11-07 18:04:30', 'D', 2, 4),
(69, '<h2>9-10月文档输出</h2><p><br></p><p> <a href=\"https://ogtd9v.yuque.com/dxnwzg/kc51bx/ldebzf2nvpxgazcx\" target=\"_blank\">event tracking</a> </p><p><br></p><p> <a href=\"https://ogtd9v.yuque.com/dxnwzg/kc51bx/lodwsuoffwutr6pg\" target=\"_blank\">dispute and complaint</a> </p>', '/public/uploads/2024/11/12/1731382567413990.jpg', '9-10月文档输出', '', '', '文档', 'REACT', '1', '2024-11-12 11:36:07', '2024-11-12 11:36:07', 'D', 2, 2),
(70, '<p><br></p>', '', '', '', '', '', 'REACT', '1', '2024-12-30 15:29:12', '2024-12-30 15:29:12', 'D', 1, 2);
INSERT INTO `blog_essay` (`id`, `html`, `coverUrl`, `title`, `subtitle`, `digest`, `tags`, `domain`, `radio`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `upt_act`, `state`, `reading_num`) VALUES
(71, '<h3>1.登录npm</h3><p>在终端登录npm，记得将镜像切换成npm官方镜像，否则无法登录，以下是几个常用的镜像，可通过nrm ls 进行查看，如果提示无法识别nrm，说明没有安装，可以全局安装nrm用来管理镜像源，npm i nrm -g &nbsp; &nbsp;或 &nbsp;yarn add nrm -g 安装这个node的版本要18以上，可以用nvm再进行切换</p><p>npm config set registry &nbsp;https://registry.npmmirror.com/</p><p> &nbsp;npm ---------- https://registry.npmjs.org/</p><p> &nbsp;yarn --------- https://registry.yarnpkg.com/</p><p> &nbsp;tencent ------ https://mirrors.tencent.com/npm/</p><p> &nbsp;cnpm --------- https://r.cnpmjs.org/</p><p> &nbsp;taobao ------- https://registry.npmmirror.com/</p><p> &nbsp;npmMirror ---- https://skimdb.npmjs.com/registry/</p><p> &nbsp;huawei ------- https://repo.huaweicloud.com/repository/npm/</p><p><br></p><p>换好镜像源之后，在终端输入npm login，如果成功，会提示你输入账号密码，因为npm的官网是外网，可以用vpn换一下ip，如果还没有自己的npm账号，可以到官网进行注册一个： <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.npmjs.com/</a> </p><p>登录之后我们就可以进行发布我们的包了</p><h3>2.发布</h3><p>在想要发布的包下用npm init 初始化一个package.json，大概的配置如下，包的名称，版本main为入口文件，</p><p><br></p><p>具体操作是：</p><p>比如我用yarn build将我需要发布的包进行构建，（记得将私有化设置成false，<span style=\"color: rgb(156, 220, 254);\">\"private\"</span><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 204, 204);\">: </span><span style=\"color: rgb(86, 156, 214);\">false</span>）这时一般会生成了一个dist文件夹，但里面是没有package文件的，在该文件夹下将这个package.json丢进去就可以进行发布了</p><pre><code >{\n  \"name\": \"joyd-demo\",\n  \"version\": \"1.1.17\",\n  \"description\": \"\",\n  \"main\": \"joyd-demo.umd.js\",\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"test\": \"echo \\\"Error: no test specified\\\" && exit 1\"\n  },\n  \"author\": \"\",\n  \"license\": \"ISC\"\n}</code></pre><p> &nbsp; &nbsp;<img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2025/01/09/173638852264410.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><p>大概的文件结构如上，joyd-demo是我构建出来的包名</p><p>然后将终端切换到该文件夹目录下，输入npm publish，网络没有问题的话应该就发布出去了</p><p>值得注意的是每发布一次需要将版本，也就是version提升一个小版本</p><p>发布后可以到官网登录查看自己发布的包。然后就可以使用自己发布的包啦</p><h3>3.使用</h3><p>比如我上传了一个包叫joyd-demo</p><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2025/01/09/1736389058264323.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 100%;\"/></p><p>通过npm i &nbsp;joyd-demo 进行下载，然后就可以使用啦</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2025/01/09/1736389264761630.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"\"/></p><p><br></p><p>我这边是自己写的一个组件库，使用后，可以在写文档站的时候直接使用这个组件库</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"http://117.50.179.27:7001/public/uploads/2025/01/09/1736389309174229.png\" alt=\"\" data-href=\"\" style=\"width: 100%;\"/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>', '/public/uploads/2025/01/10/1736493490041614.png', '如何上传自己的包到npm', '上传npm', '如果你想要将自己的组件库或者自己写的一些公共方法，框架，api或者说react的公共hook，就可以上传到npm，之后你的项目就可以像下载其他依赖一样去下载你自己的东西', 'npm', '其他', '1', '2025-01-09 10:22:26', '2025-01-09 10:22:26', 'U', 1, 32);

-- --------------------------------------------------------

--
-- 表的结构 `blog_record`
--

CREATE TABLE `blog_record` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL COMMENT '主键',
  `created_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '创建时间',
  `updated_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '更新时间',
  `message` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '记录内容',
  `upt_act` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '字段状态，U表示更新，D表示已删除，I表示正常'
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

--
-- 转存表中的数据 `blog_record`
--

